 While the coefficients of other sources seem unchanged, the 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta_{1}$
\end_inset

 increases over time, from 0.231 in 1970s to 0.6 in 2000s.
 It is consistent with more share issue trend over time, about 8 times compared
 to 1970s.
 The share issue is pro-cyclical, drop in recessions 1991, 2001, 2008.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
